oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Art of Joyful Living
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Azar, Steve; Rose, Kristi; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (teal on yellow) announcing "The Art of Joyful Living," concert and silent auction benefiting Christ the King School, featuring Steve Azar, Kristi Rose and Fats Kaplin, Emerson Hart, the Big Happy, and Kent Blazy at the Mercy Lounge on January 28. Poster features woodcuts of stars.
